title: Kill and Kill Again [1981 - South Africa] action
description:
Kill and Kill Again (1981 - South Africa, USA)

Action / Drama

starring . . . . James Ryan, Anneline Kriel, Michael Mayer
 
http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0082612/


Anneline Kriel became 1974's Miss World at age 19 representing South Africa

Crime-fighting martial artist and secret agent Steve Chase is recruited by beautiful blonde Kandy Kane to save her father, Dr Horatio Kane, a noted scientist who has developed a new, powerful serum capable of total mind control. It turns out Dr Kane is in the clutches of the evil Marduk, a baddie with an army of henchmen and karate-trained underlings in his Middle Eastern camp. Steve Chase assembles his own squad and they promptly head out to kick some evildoers in the butt.
